<abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Autograph Draft Signed: a draft of a letter or document in the handwriting of, and signed by, the author ]">ADfS</abbr>, <span class="ref-rep">PWacD</span>.
</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-02-02-0375-0001-fn-0001-ptr" id="GEWN-03-02-02-0375-0001-fn-0001">1</a>
	
   <p>For Joseph Trumbulls proposals regarding pork and beef, see <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-01-02-0315" class="document">his letter to GW of 6 September</a>. For Congresss directions on this subject, see minutes for 20 Oct. in the Proceedings of the Committee of Conference, 1824 Oct. 1775, <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-02-02-0175-0003" class="document">Document II, Minutes of the Conference</a>, and <span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ Worthington Chauncey Ford et al., eds. &lt;i&gt;Journals of the Continental Congress, 1774-1789&lt;/i&gt;. 34 vols. Washington, D.C., 190437. ]"><span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">JCC</span>,</span> 3:273, 323.</p>

</div>
<span class="pb center" title="page number in print edition (no page scan available)" id="GEWN-03-02-02-pb-0412">[412]</span>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-02-02-0375-0001-fn-0002-ptr" id="GEWN-03-02-02-0375-0001-fn-0002">2</a>

   <p>Trumbull is probably referring to GWs letter to him of 2 November.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-02-02-0375-0001-fn-0003-ptr" id="GEWN-03-02-02-0375-0001-fn-0003">3</a>

   <p>See <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-02-02-0375-0002" class="document">enclosure</a><span class="choice deletion" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover_choice ] header=[]  body=[ Deleted: ' printed below' &lt;span style='font-size: 90%'&gt;[[2014-12-02]]&lt;/span&gt; ]"><img alt="deletion" src="images/deletion_mark-trans.png" style="border:none;vertical-align: text-bottom; padding-right:2px"/></span>.</p>

